<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">詩</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">秋夕寄友僧</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<lb ed="X" n="0931c11"/><milestone unit="juan" n="45"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c12"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a05"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="45"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="45"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>閑居編第四十五</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c14"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a06"/><byline cb:type="author">宋孤山沙門　智圓　著</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">陳宮</cb:mulu><head>陳宮</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a08"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0931c1701"><l>龍盤虎踞景堪尋</l><l>王氣消亡信禍淫</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a09"/><l>結綺臨春何處是</l><l>數聲啼鳥暮煙深</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">春日別同志</cb:mulu><head>春日別同志</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a11"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0931c2001"><l>路岐南北與東西</l><l>竚立遲遲惜解擕</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a12"/><l>忍向離亭折楊柳</l><l><g ref="#CB15085">𣆶</g>花零落杜<g ref="#CB15102">䳌</g>啼</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">夏日湖上寄太白長老</cb:mulu><head>夏日湖上寄太白長老</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a14"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0931c2301"><l>風撼芙蕖入座香</l><l>水軒閑坐趣何長</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0931c24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a15"/><l>相懷不是人間景</l><l>隔岸歸禽噪晚涼</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0932a" n="0932a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">西湖</cb:mulu><head>西湖</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a17"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a0201"><l>清帶月華涵竹戶</l><l>冷澄秋色照禪衣</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184a18"/><l>滔滔潤物知多少</l><l>極目寒波瀁落暉</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送禪者</cb:mulu><head>送禪者</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b02"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a0501"><l>祖意曾明萬事閑</l><l>誰云方外與人間</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b03"/><l>卷衣江上秋來別</l><l>處處禪心朵朵山</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">古意</cb:mulu><head>古意</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b05"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a0801"><l>登山伐樵柯忽折</l><l>臨井汲泉綆仍絕</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b06"/><l>音信不來無處說</l><l>朔風飄飄滿天雪</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">雲</cb:mulu><head>雲</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b08"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a1101"><l>冷照碧潭閑不極</l><l>靜當青漢影彌分</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b09"/><l>卷舒終合為霖雨</l><l>不向陽臺惑楚君</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">苔錢三首</cb:mulu><head>苔錢三首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b11"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a1401"><l>夷甫不言非爾類</l><l>魯<g ref="#CB17051">󴊛</g>為論偶同名</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b12"/><l>秋來自滿虗閑地</l><l>不用良工鼓鑄成</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b14"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a1701"><l>求多未必增貪<g ref="#CB15137">𥪰</g></l><l>委積唯堪貰寂寥</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b15"/><l>顏子黔婁舊居畔</l><l>亂鋪平地伴逍遙</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b17"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a2001"><l>鑪冶只應憑陋巷</l><l>富饒應不是豪家</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0184b18"/><l><g ref="#CB15085">𣆶</g>來雨歇茆堂外</l><l>散在閑庭買落花</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其三</cb:mulu><head>其三</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">自遣三首</cb:mulu><head>自遣三首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932a24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a03"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932a2401"><l>古屋苔荒疾乍瘳</l><l>前村林木覺先秋</l>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0932b" n="0932b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a04"/><l>野塘日暮搘筇立</l><l>雲自無依水自流</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其一</cb:mulu><head>其一</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a06"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932b0301"><l>講退時時學苦吟</l><l>人間聲利<anchor xml:id="beg_a6" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_a6"/>無心</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a07"/><l>水邊占得清閑景</l><l>雨霽遙峰夜月深</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a09"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932b0601"><l>不惑年猶欠四年</l><l>道情高趣恥前賢</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a10"/><l>清風明月知多少</l><l>謾學廬山種白蓮</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">其三</cb:mulu><head>其三</head></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送僧</cb:mulu><head>送僧</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a13"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932b1001"><l>萬緣難繫自由身</l><l>道性何妨學世人</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a14"/><l>擬向東門贈離別</l><l>長堤楊柳未成春</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">庭竹</cb:mulu><head>庭竹</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a16"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932b1301"><l>移去羣花種此君</l><l>滿庭寒翠更無塵</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a17"/><l>暑天閑遶煩襟盡</l><l>猶有清風借四鄰</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">雞</cb:mulu><head>雞</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b01"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932b1601"><l>簷前棲息傍蒿叢</l><l>風雨司晨爾有功</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b02"/><l>鸚鵡無能憑<g ref="#CB02439">󰦇</g>舌</l><l>侯門翻得養金籠</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送僧之金陵</cb:mulu><head>送僧之金陵</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b04"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932b1901"><l>金錫孤<g ref="#CB06078">𢹂</g>問去程</l><l>萋萋原草暮煙平</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b05"/><l>六朝舊跡秦淮畔</l><l>應感興亡聽水聲</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">出道場山途中作</cb:mulu><head>出道場山途中作</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b07"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932b2201"><l>獨下層巒景物秋</l><l>依依雲木似相留</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b08"/><l>孤舟曉汎平波去</l><l>更為青山一轉頭</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932b24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">將之霅溪寄別擇梧師</cb:mulu><head>將之霅溪寄別擇梧師</head>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0932c" n="0932c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b10"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932c0101"><l>白雲深處草堂閑</l><l>曾伴支公薄暮還</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b11"/><l>獨上孤舟欲西去</l><l>倚檣迴望只青山</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄淨慈寺悟真師</cb:mulu><head>寄淨慈寺悟真師</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b13"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932c0401"><l>憶得涼宵宿上方</l><l>靜吟閑話趣何長</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b14"/><l>別來音信無由寄</l><l>目斷遙天鴈一行</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">次韻詶梵天闍梨</cb:mulu><head>次韻詶梵天闍梨</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b16"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932c0701"><l>數峰殘雪對閑門</l><l>世態悠悠莫可論</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b17"/><l>靜室禪餘忽相憶</l><l>劃<g ref="#CB01926">󰞆</g>孤坐到黃昏</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0185b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">溪居即事寄梵天闍梨</cb:mulu><head>溪居即事寄梵天闍梨</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a01"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932c1001"><l>松竹森森獨掩扉</l><l>塵中誰復愛忘機</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a02"/><l>蒼苔滿砌無人到</l><l>猶感幽禽夜夜歸</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">武康溪居即事寄寶印大師四首</cb:mulu><head>武康溪居即事寄寶印大師四首</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a04"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0932c1301"><l>偶來溪上縱閑吟</l><l>泉石深藏便有心</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0932c14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0186a05"/><l>莫擬他年訪幽跡</l><l>白雲青嶂更難尋</l></lg>
